Hey guys.
Hi.  I think plan 2 is the best.  There wouldn't be any waste disposal cost or carbon tax, and they would get really good tax breaks.

plan 1 is the only plan that fits into their "tight" budget.

its 21 million above budget

Plan 2 has no taxes.
